test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:

 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7f8992949cc0> = [[1, 85, 1, 85, 1, 85], [], [85, 1, 85, 1, 85], [], [85, 1, 85, 1, 85], [], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 52200625 == 85
 +  where 52200625 = <built-in function prod>([1, 5, 17, 85, 1, 5, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
